# description
keyboard shortcuts, tips and tricks for google sheets

# notes
https://support.google.com/docs/answer/181110?hl=en&co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop#zippy=%2Cmac-shortcuts

# help
Show_keyb_shortcuts	⌘+/

# Basics
Select-col	Ctrl+Spc
Select-row	Sh+Spc
Select-all	⌘+a | ⌘+Sh+Spc
Undo	⌘+z
Redo	⌘+y |⌘+Sh+z|Fn+F4
Find	⌘+f
Find_and_replace	⌘+Sh+h
Fill_range	⌘+Enter
Fill_down	⌘+d
Fill_right	⌘+r
Save	⌘+s
Open	⌘+o
Print	⌘+p
Copy	⌘+c
Cut	⌘+x
Paste	⌘+v
Paste_values_only	⌘+Sh+v
Insert_new_sheet	Sh+Fn+F11
Compact_controls	Ctrl+Sh+f
Input_tools_on/off	⌘+Sh+k
Select_input_tools	⌘+Opt+Sh+k
Tool_finder	Opt+/
Select_current_region_around_selected_cell	⌘+Sh+* |Ctrl+Sh+*
Display_or_hide_menus	⌘+Opt+R | Ctrl+Sh+F

