# Notes and COmments
Insert/edit_note	Sh+F2
Insert/edit_comment	⌘+Opt+m
Open_comment_discussion_thread	⌘+Opt+Sh+a
Enter_current_comment	holding_Ctrl+⌘,e,c
Move_to_next_comment	holding Ctrl+⌘,n,c
Move_to_previous_comment	holding Ctrl+⌘,p,c

# Use_keyboard_shortcuts_on_selected_comments
Reply_to_current_comment	R
Move_to_next_comment	J
Move_to_previous_comment	K
Resolve_current_comment	E
Exit_current_comment	U

# Menus
File_menu	Ctrl+Opt+f
Edit_menu	Ctrl+Opt+e
View_menu	Ctrl+Opt+v
Insert_menu	Ctrl+Opt+i
Format_menu	Ctrl+Opt+o
Data_menu	Ctrl+Opt+d
Tools_menu	Ctrl+Opt+t
Open_insert_menu	⌘+Opt+= (with cells selected)
Open delete_menu	⌘+Opt+- (with cells selected)
Form_menu(present when the spreadsheet is connected to a form)	Ctrl+Opt+m
Add-ons_menu	Ctrl+Opt+n
Help menu	Ctrl+Opt+h
Sheet_menu(copy, delete, and other sheet actions)	Opt+Sh+s
Context menu ⌘+Sh+\ | Sh+F10

Table_col_menu	⌘+Opt+\

# Rows / Cols
Insert_rows_above ⌘+Opt+= (with rows selected)Ctrl+Opt+i,r,r
Insert_rows_below	Ctrl+Opt+i,r,b
Insert_cols to_the_left  ⌘+Opt+= (with cols selected)Ctrl+Opt+i,c,c
Insert_cols_to_the_right	Ctrl+Opt+i,c,o
Delete_rows	⌘+Opt+- (with rows selected)Ctrl+Opt+e,,d
Delete_cols	⌘+Opt+- (with cols selected)Ctrl+Opt+e,,e
Hide_row	⌘+Opt+9
Unhide_row	⌘+Sh+9
Hide_col	⌘+Opt+0
Unhide_col	⌘+Sh+0
Group_rows_or_cols	Opt+Sh+RArrow
Ungroup_rows_or_cols	Opt+Sh+LArrow
Expand_grouped_rows_or_cols	Opt+Sh+DownArrow
Collapse_grouped_rows_or_cols	Opt+Sh+UpArrow

# Formulas
